description:
Recorded between 1963-2019, Degrees Of Freedom Found is a six CD set “Blue” Gene Tyranny hand selected from archival, live recordings, and brand new first recordings before his passing in 2020.

title_full:
Antonina Nowacka

            —
            Vocal Sketches From Oaxaca

label: Mica Levi
description:
Ever-unpredictable genius Mica Levi sports a wickedly loose new album following hot on the heels of that Ruff Dog pearl just a few weeks ago.

It appears that the award-winning composer is here joined by their Curl collective in ‘Blue Alibi’ for an album that almost preternaturally collapses the vernacular of grunge rock, free jazz, indie-pop, rap, and chamber... more
